contracts.name: KintoAppRegistry
contracts.description: Central system contract defining addresses that are allowed to be called by EOAs. The modified Kinto node reads this configuration and drops all other transactions from EOAs. Accordingly, users can only transact from their smart wallets.

contracts.name: KintoWalletBeacon_implemention
contracts.description: Implementation for all KintoWallets, managed by a beacon proxy.

contracts.name: KintoID
contracts.description: Manages Kinto's KYC system: KYC provider addresses and the KYC status of users.
